702158f-a.title: Bronx: White Plains Road - 228th Street (East)
702158f-a.text:
White Plains Road, at the N.E. corner of East 228th Street (right).
The 3-story frame house, slightly east of the corner, bears No. 705 on
the latter street.
May 24, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
